    "description": "What would happen if an insane wizard set up shop on a cursed island and decided to blend the dark arts of <strong>necromancy</strong> and ... <strong>nostalgia</strong>?<br><br>They'd become a Retromancer. And you'd have to hunt them down; probably in some kind of intense, pixelated, twin stick shooter.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Champion</h2><br>Select one of four different characters to match your play style: Barbarian, Mage, Hunter, or Cleric,<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arm Yourself Against the Madness</h2><br>Unlock weapon drops and permanent upgrades between games that enhance each character's strengths: mages get even more rapid fire, clerics get more blessings from their gods, hunters become even more deadly at range, and barbarians yell louder than ever before!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defy Death</h2><br>A unique death's door mechanic gives you a fighting chance to come back from the brink of death.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enlist Your Friends</h2><br>Grab up to three friends in the local 4-player co-op mode.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive The Journey</h2><br>Battle through 30 stages spread across 6 areas: Endure a plague of locusts in the haunted woods, overthrow a cultist army in the ruins, surrender your sanity to the creatures of the Void, and kill the Retromancer.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007180/extras/ae6524eb089b05218ad5b919eaaf7be8.poster.avif?t=1635638289\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007180/extras/ae6524eb089b05218ad5b919eaaf7be8.webm?t=1635638289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007180/extras/ae6524eb089b05218ad5b919eaaf7be8.mp4?t=1635638289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
